{"title":"Yakima goes premium w/ new StageTwo tray rack, carries more than just MTB w/ new HangTight","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/10/19/yakima-goes-premium-w-new-stage-2-tray-rack-carries-more-than-just-mtb-w-new-hangtight/","date":1634663985000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165419/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor5.jpg\" data-fancybox=\"\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165419/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor5-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165419/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor5-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165419/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor5-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165419/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor5-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165419/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor5-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165419/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor5.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></a><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-274933\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>It’s taken a while, but it seems like bike racks in the U.S. are catching up to their European counterparts. Well, at least in terms of lighting, that is. That’s probably because having lights and a license plate holder isn’t a requirement in many parts of the U.S.—or it is a requirement, but generally isn’t enforced. However, to improve vehicle safety when carrying bikes, and give police one less reason to potentially pull you over, more brands stateside are offering racks with integrated lighting—like the new Yakima Stage 2 with the optional Safety Nate package.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165421/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor6.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165421/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor6.jpg\" alt=\"Yakima Stage 2 tray hitch rack \" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165421/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor6.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165421/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor6-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165421/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor6-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165421/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor6-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165421/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor6-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>Yakima is taking an interesting route here, as the lights aren’t included in the base model Stage 2. Instead, they’re offered as an additional accessory package that sells for $219. That package includes full rear lighting with tail, brake, and turn signal lights along with a rear license plate light for the external license plate bracket. We’ve seen new racks with lights from <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/08/10/new-kuat-piston-pro-x-hitch-rack-gets-kashima-coat-onetap-hydro-arms-led-lights/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Kuat</a> and <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/10/19/motorized-saris-door-county-bike-rack-is-easier-to-load-heavy-bikes-plus-new-4-in-1-thru-axle-adapter/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Saris</a> recently, but both of those omit the rear license plate holder which may or may not be needed. The whole point to any of this is that a bike on a bike rack can block your taillights and license plate. Repositioning them keeps them visible, and keeps you legal depending on the local laws.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165423/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor7.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165423/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor7.jpg\" alt=\"Yakima Stage 2 tray hitch rack wiring\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165423/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor7.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165423/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor7-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165423/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor7-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165423/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor7-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165423/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor7-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165430/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor10.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165430/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor10.jpg\" alt=\"Yakima Stage 2 tray hitch rack wiring\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165430/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor10.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165430/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor10-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165430/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor10-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165430/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor10-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165430/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor10-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>The Safety Nate uses a standard flat 4-way connector, and the wiring harness routes through the frame of the rack.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165447/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor18.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165447/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor18.jpg\" alt=\"Yakima Stage 2 tray hitch rack wiring harness\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165447/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor18.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165447/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor18-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165447/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor18-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165447/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor18-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165447/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor18-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>Due to the positioning of the lights, Yakima designed them to rotate 90° so that they’re still visible when the rack is folded up.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165436/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor13.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165436/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor13.jpg\" alt=\"Yakima Stage 2 tray hitch rack grey\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165436/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor13.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165436/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor13-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165436/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor13-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165436/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor13-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165436/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor13-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>For those that don’t want the lights, the new Stage 2 tray style rack will be sold without the Safety Nate package and starts at $749. The rack gets a premium Anthracite or Vapor Grey finish, and a few updates that position it at the top of the Yakima range.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165434/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor12.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165434/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor12.jpg\" alt=\"Yakima Stage 2 tray hitch rack vertical\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165434/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor12.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165434/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor12-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165434/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor12-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165434/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor12-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165434/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor12-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165439/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor14.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165439/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor14.jpg\" alt=\"Yakima Stage 2 tray hitch rack two way handle\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165439/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor14.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165439/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor14-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165439/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor14-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165439/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor14-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165439/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor14-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>A new tilt lever offers access on either side of the handle for easy access in either position.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165449/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor19.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165449/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor19.jpg\" alt=\"Yakima Stage 2 tray hitch rack speed knob\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165449/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor19.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165449/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor19-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165449/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor19-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165449/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor19-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165449/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor19-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>There’s also an updated speed knob that tightens the rack down in the hitch and locks it to the vehicle with their SKS (Single Key System).</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165432/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor11.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165432/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor11.jpg\" alt=\"Yakima Stage 2 tray hitch rack upright lock\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165432/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor11.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165432/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor11-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165432/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor11-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165432/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor11-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165432/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor11-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165445/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor17.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165445/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor17.jpg\" alt=\"Yakima Stage 2 tray hitch rack lock loop\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165445/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor17.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165445/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor17-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165445/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor17-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165445/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor17-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165445/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor17-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>Locking is also available for each bike with SKS cable locks at each upright, and there’s an additional lock loop on the body of the rack to add a burly chain lock for secure storage when you need it.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165451/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor20.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165451/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor20.jpg\" alt=\"Yakima Stage 2 tray hitch rack tire strap\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165451/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor20.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165451/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor20-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165451/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor20-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165451/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor20-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165451/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor20-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165453/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor21.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165453/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor21.jpg\" alt=\"Yakima Stage 2 tray hitch rack front wheel cradle\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165453/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor21.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165453/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor21-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165453/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor21-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165453/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor21-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165453/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor21-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>Each tray is positioned with ‘stadium tiering’ and staggered trays to make loading multiple bikes easier. The trays have a 52″ maximum wheelbase, and will fit up to 3.25″ tires before you’ll need the additional fat bike strap for bigger tires. In terms of the weight limit, Yakima has two levels: there is a 60lb maximum tray capability which is rated for RV use, or a 42lb tray rating for off-road use. A two bike add-on will be offered in each color for another $549.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165428/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor9.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165428/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor9.jpg\" alt=\"Yakima Stage 2 tray hitch rack ramp up accessory\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165428/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor9.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165428/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor9-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165428/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor9-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165428/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor9-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165428/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor9-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>There will also be a Ramp Up accessory offered for $99. This ramp connects to the tray and allows you to push your bike up the ramp into the rack for easier loading. It does not store on the rack, so you’ll need to install and remove this every time you want to use it while storing it inside the vehicle between use.</p><h2>HangTight 4 or 6 Bike Rack</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165458/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor23.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165458/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor23.jpg\" alt=\"Yakima HangTight bike rack \" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165458/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor23.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165458/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor23-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165458/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor23-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165458/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor23-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165458/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor23-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>Want to carry more bikes and more types of bikes than the current <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2018/07/27/yakima-hangover-hauls-heavy-duty-vertical-bike-racks-for-trucks-the-vanlife/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">HangOver</a>? Then you might want to check out the new HangTight. Like the HangOver, the HangTight supports each bike vertically which allows up to 6 bikes to be carried on the back of your vehicle with a 2″ hitch.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165500/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor24.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165500/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor24.jpg\" alt=\"Yakima HangTight bike rack handlebar cradle\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165500/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor24.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165500/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor24-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165500/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor24-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165500/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor24-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165500/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor24-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165502/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor25.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165502/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor25.jpg\" alt=\"Yakima HangTight bike rack handlebar cradle\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165502/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor25.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165502/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor25-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165502/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor25-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165502/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor25-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165502/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor25-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165506/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor27.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165506/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor27.jpg\" alt=\"Yakima HangTight bike rack tire strap\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165506/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor27.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165506/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor27-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165506/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor27-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165506/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor27-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165506/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor27-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>However, where the HangOver supported only suspension forks on the fork crown, the HangTight attaches to the bars on either side of the stem. That allows for the rack to work with many more bikes with rigid or suspension forks. Obviously, there will be some bikes that won’t work with this arrangement (tri bikes?), but it should work with more bikes than the HangOver.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165512/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor30.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165512/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor30.jpg\" alt=\"Yakima HangTight bike rack for sprinter van transit\" width=\"800\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165512/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor30.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165512/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor30-200x300.jpg 200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165512/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor30-80x120.jpg 80w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165512/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor30-768x1152.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></a></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165510/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor29.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165510/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor29.jpg\" alt=\"Yakima HangTight bike rack tilt mechanism\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165510/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor29.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165510/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor29-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165510/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor29-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165510/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor29-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165510/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor29-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>It will also work with more vehicles than the HangOver thanks to the flat profile of the bike arrangement. That means for flat back vehicles like Sprinter vans, it will work better, and still offer tilt-down access.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165456/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor22.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165456/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor22.jpg\" alt=\"Yakima HangTight bike rack 4 or 6 bike\" width=\"800\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165456/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor22.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165456/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor22-200x300.jpg 200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165456/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor22-80x120.jpg 80w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165456/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor22-768x1152.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></a></p><p>Yakima says that the HangTight will&nbsp;<em>not</em> replace the HangOver, but will be offered alongside for $799 for the 4 bike or $999 for the 6 bike version. Expect these to be available before the end of the year.</p><h2>Updated GateKeeper Preview</h2><h2><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165417/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor4.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165417/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor4.jpg\" alt=\"Yakima GateKeeper truck tailgate pad\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165417/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor4.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165417/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor4-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165417/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor4-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165417/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor4-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165417/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor4-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></h2><p>In the back of their booth, Yakima was also giving a sneak peek at the updated GateKeeper truck tailgate pad.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165411/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165411/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor1.jpg\" alt=\"Yakima GateKeeper truck tailgate pad strap\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165411/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor1.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165411/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor1-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165411/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor1-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165411/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor1-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165411/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor1-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>It will still hold up to five bikes, but one of the biggest updates is the move from velcro straps to buckles for the frame holds.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165415/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165415/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor3.jpg\" alt=\"Yakima GateKeeper truck tailgate pad for Jeep Gladiator\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165415/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor3.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165415/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor3-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165415/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor3-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165415/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor3-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/14165415/Yakima-Hang-Tight-Stage-2-bike-racks-updated-truck-tailgate-pad-cover-2022-Sea-Otter-Classic-2021-Bikerumor3-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>The shape has also been updated, specifically to fit the new Jeep Gladiator pickups, and a lock loop has been added for additional security.</p><p><a href=\"https://yakima.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>yakima.com</em></a></p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Zach Overholt","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"83fb053362286b45789eb3bd054f07d3103cba796eb18eb264a959ee71377a99","category":"Cycling"}